---
title: Roast Cauliflower, Chicken & Goat Cheese Salad with Israeli Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Like a soft teddy bear, tonight’s dish is fluffy and calming. Tufts of roasted cauliflower, chicken and other warm veggies poke
out of a golden Israeli couscous, mixed with creamy goat cheese on top, it will be like eating a very tasty cloud.
